nausea and unusual fatigue.

236
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:45,160
Lots of doctors miss that.
Look what happened to Katherine Leon,

237
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:48,000
who went to the ER
with serious heart problems...

238
00:13:48,560 --> 00:13:51,600
The young doctor came in,
very condescending,

239
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:54,440
