266
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:20,400
Which is, sex and gender bias
can clearly distort medical outcomes.

267
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:23,440
But they are not the only forms
of bias that can do that.

268
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:27,440
