354
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:42,680
Absolutely.

355
00:20:42,840 --> 00:20:49,840
What happens is you start to develop
fear around going to the doctor.

356
00:20:50,560 --> 00:20:53,560
Yeah, of course you'd be
